'''白島'''（{{lang-en|White Island}}，{{lang-tl|Puting Pulo}}）是一座[[沙洲|沙洲]]，位於[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[卡米金省|卡米金省]][[曼巴豪|曼巴豪]]外海。該島長約1.4公里，形狀約略似[[馬蹄|馬蹄]]，島上並無樹木。<ref>[http://hawaiianwebmaster.com/attractions.html "Landmarks and Tourist Attractions"] {{Wayback|url=http://hawaiianwebmaster.com/attractions.html |date=20110809003936 }}. Camiguin: A Tropical Paradise. Retrieved on 2011-08-04.</ref>該島每年約有千名[[觀光客|觀光客]]到訪，遊客多數搭乘[[舢舨|舢舨]]及[[螃蟹船|螃蟹船]]等[[交通工具|交通工具]]前往，部分[[度假村|度假村]]提供[[旅遊|旅遊]]行程，以私人船隻接送遊客。<ref>[http://www.silent-gardens.com/camiguin-white.php "White Island"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830050504/http://www.silent-gardens.com/camiguin-white.php |date=2011-08-30 }}. Visayan Silent Gardens. Retrieved on 2011-08-04.</ref>

